## How to Run

> [!IMPORTANT]
> You must activate the `nlp_env` conda environment. The base conda Python doesn't have the packages.

```bash
# Activate the correct environment
conda activate /Users/amaansiddiqui/miniconda3/envs/nlp_env

# Get a free Groq API key at https://console.groq.com/
echo "GROQ_API_KEY=your_key_here" > /Users/amaansiddiqui/Desktop/vine-agent/.env

cd /Users/amaansiddiqui/Desktop/vine-agent

# Run 5 benchmark agricultural queries (zero downloads needed)
python main.py --demo

# Interactive chatbot mode
python main.py --chat

# Single query
python main.py --query "Should I irrigate Block A? VWC is 19%."

# Verbose mode: see ContextPriority routing + assembled context
python main.py --demo --verbose

# Use smarter model for solver (Phase 2 — same cost, much better synthesis)
python main.py --demo --solver-llm groq --solver-model llama-3.1-70b-versatile

# Use stress scenario for sensor simulator
python main.py --demo --sensor-scenario stress
```

